CARBON_HOME/lib contains all the libraries necessary to run Carbon in
standalone mode

1. endorsed
   Endorsed Java libraries

2. tomcat
   Carbon uses embedded Tomcat when running in standalone mode. Embedded
   Tomcat & its dependencies, and other dependencies needed to startup the
   standalone Carbon server, are located in this directory.

3. log4j.properties
   The log4j.properties file used by Carbon

4. README
   This file

5. core
   Contains the Carbon web application   

6. api
   Contains common libraries for OSGi environment and web applications

7. patches
   Directory to include patches for root level libraries

8. transactions.properties
   Atomikos properties file      
